  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will build community based behaviour change communication system to generate the awareness at community level on toilet use, hand wash at critical timings and menstrual hygiene management  in 20 villages of Barabanki district of  Uttar Pradesh in India.Project will build skills of community volunteers, adolescent girls groups and women groups on behaviour change messages, communication tools and participatory methods for mobilizing the community, tracking behaviour changes.</narrative>
